        "content": "<p>I'm looking to find the path to the installed documentation (e.g. <code>/opt/julias/julia-1.7.3/share/doc/julia/html/en</code>), but I'm not sure how to go about it.</p>",
        "id": 284289486,
        "sender_full_name": "Timothy",
        "timestamp": 1653835511
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>how did you install julia?</p>",
        "id": 284289500,
        "sender_full_name": "Sukera",
        "timestamp": 1653835539
    },
    {
        "content": "<p><code>joinpath(Sys.BINDIR, \"..\", \"share\", \"doc\", \"julia\", \"html\", \"en\")</code></p>",
        "id": 284291322,
        "sender_full_name": "Fredrik Ekre",
        "timestamp": 1653838286
    },
