    {
        "content": "<p>For reference, this has helped with <a href=\"https://github.com/tecosaur/HelpfulErrors.jl/commit/6f6cf3ad60b2861160c82bb2bc2503b11a8fbbe0\">https://github.com/tecosaur/HelpfulErrors.jl/commit/6f6cf3ad60b2861160c82bb2bc2503b11a8fbbe0</a></p>",
        "id": 284292836,
        "sender_full_name": "Timothy",
        "timestamp": 1653840635
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>Note that this won't necessarily work if you compiled from source (which is why I asked :) )</p>",
        "id": 284293136,
        "sender_full_name": "Sukera",
        "timestamp": 1653841087
    },
    {
        "content": "<p>if you compile from source, by default you don't have built docs installed - you have to run <code>make docs</code>, which builds them in the julia repo locally</p>",
